title: HBH Vilnius
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Juice bar, European, Lithuanian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Traditional Lithuanian restaurant offers a few vegan items and can also veganize other dishes. Vegan dishes to be made upon request are couscous with veggies in tomato sauce; grilled veggie skewer with couscous; plain salad with seed mix (olive-lemon oil as sauce). Some sides are also vegan, as are some of the juices. Plant based milks available for coffee. Hot chocolate might have traces of milk.
